  "description": {
    "zh": "哈，你又来了。终于决定抱紧我这根大腿了？真够给劲啊。我需要在我的地盘里搞出点动静来。那些外来的人一直骑在我头上拉屎，搅黄我的生意，他们胡乱开枪，抢劫我的手下，毫不留情的虐杀我的人。这让我有点不爽，这么说吧，这跟我的经营理念相差甚远。你一定得使用手枪来解决他们，这样他们才会知道自己是在跟一个高手作对。好了，去把他们全解决掉吧，我会按照每个人头给你赏金，甚至还会给你一笔额外的谢礼。日子艰难，时间紧迫，但是你总得找条路子活下去——等你的好消息。",
    "en": "Ah, it's you again. Decided to hang on tight to me then, ye? Bloody awesome. I need to stir up some movement in our region. All sorts of outsiders keep popping up meddling with business, shoot, loot valuables off my guys, whack them indiscriminately. That makes me kinda unhappy, so to say, and it does not fall in line with my business concept. And to make it clear that they're in deep shit, fuck them up with pistols, let them understand that the pros are working. Well, go on and rake them \"operators\" of yours, and I’ll pay the bounty for each head, and even something extra as a present on top. Times are hard, and you have to make a living here somehow - preferably a good one."
  },
